description: This small trattoria hidden among the canals in the countryside is run by a couple of partners who showcase the specialities of the region with professionalism and enthusiasm. The menu includes delicacies such as fish and vegetable couscous, and sfoglia pastry with cream and flakes of chocolate, as well as a few more modern dishes.
